higdon <- function(x) {
  i <- which(x <= 0.6)
  x[i] <- 2 * sin(pi * 0.8 * x[i] * 4) + 0.4 * cos(pi * 0.8 * x[i] * 16)
  x[-i] <- 2 * x[-i] - 1
  return(x)
}
